node.text:
In the centenary year of the House, Gucci celebrated its Aria collection through a special fashion show held at the Shanghai Exhibition Centre in China, recreating the set and atmosphere of the #GucciAria film, co-directed by @floriasigismondi and @alessandro_michele, which debuted earlier this year in April. 
#AlessandroMichele
Music:
The soundtrack, by Alessandro Michele and mixed by Lawrence Rothman, comprises a selection of songs 
featuring the word Gucci, speaking to the staying power of the Maison and how profusely it contributed to 
the vocabulary of pop culture.
Lil Pump "Gucci Gang”
(B. Murray / G. Garcia / G. G. Nealy)
Rick Ross feat. Future “Green Gucci Suit”
(R. Ross / A. Stewart / N. Wilburn / D. Hayes)

Bhad Bhabie “Gucci Flip Flops (feat. Lil Yachty)”
(M. McCollum / L. Jae / I. Whitlow / J. Muhammad / L. Porter / D. McCorkell / D. Bregoli / S. Gloade / J. 
Lowe)
Mier “Gucci On My Bag”
Die Antwoord, Dita Von Teese “Gucci Coochie”
(A. Du Toit / W. Jones / J. Nobrega / L. Muggard / Dita Von Teese)
Vitalic, feat. David Shaw “Waiting For The Stars”
(P. Arbez / D. Shaw/ J. Garraud)

node.title: Gucci Aria Fashion Show in Shanghai

node.text:
Named Hortus Deliciarum (Latin for ‘Garden of Delights’), the new #GucciHighJewelry collection draws on the symbolic motifs that are dear to @alessandro_michele and Gucci, taken from the extensive and multifarious canon of House iconography. The saturated, hypnotic hues of a sky at sunset, the romanticism of a rose garden, and motifs from animal kingdom, evoking mythic bestiary and ancient fauna, are 
the ultimate source of inspiration for the new collection, including more than 130 pieces, mainly one of a kind.

node.title: The New Hortus Deliciarum High Jewelry Collection

node.text: The façade of the #GUCCIGAOK flagship store, designed by artist SeungMo Park @HANDLE, is inspired by an imaginary forest. The artist explores the interplay between light and shadow, and the application of wire netting layers results in a vivid symbolism, illustrating the boundaries between what is real and what is an illusion. Reflecting on the environmental issues of our time, the Park expresses the existence and non-existence of nature, his concerns of what can be lost, leaving only the illusion of what might be left. #AlessandroMichele

node.title: Artist SeungMo Park on creating the #GUCCIGAOK façade

node.text:
Debuting in a special film co-directed by award-winning photographer and director @floriasigismondi and @alessandro_michele, Aria. A singular voice, taking its turn in the spotlight; in the Italian language, ‘air’. In his notes on the collection, the Creative Director calls it “a deep and ecstatic diving in everything we yearningly miss today… a jubilee of breath.” 
In the year of Gucci’s centenary, Alessandro Michele opens the locks of history, only to find a deeply personal vision of the mythology that surrounds the brand. Standing sentinel is the Savoy Club—a tribute to @thesavoylondon hotel where founder Guccio Gucci worked as a liftboy in his youth. Once inside, Aria’s “hacking lab made of incursions and metamorphoses”—from Alessandro Michele’s notes on the show—is unveiled, featuring elements from House heritage and designs from @demnagvasalia, Creative Director of @balenciaga, ultimately expressions of reverence and homage.
#GucciAria #AlessandroMichele 
Music:
The soundtrack, by Alessandro Michele and mixed by Lawrence Rothman, comprises a selection of songs featuring the word Gucci, speaking to the staying power of the Maison and how profusely it contributed to the vocabulary of pop culture.
Lil Pump ‘Gucci Gang’
(B. Murray/G. Garcia/G. G. Nealy)
Rick Ross feat. Future ‘Green Gucci Suit’
(R. Ross/A. Stewart/N. Wilburn/D. Hayes)
Bhad Bhabie ‘Gucci Flip Flops (feat. Lil Yachty)’
(M. McCollum/L. Jae/I. Whitlow/J. Muhammad/L. Porter/D. McCorkell/D. Bregoli/S. Gloade/J. Lowe)
Mier ‘Gucci On My Bag’
Die Antwoord, Dita Von Teese ‘Gucci Coochie’
(A. Du Toit/W. Jones/J. Nobrega/L. Muggard/Dita Von Teese)
Vitalic, feat. David Shaw and The Beat ‘Waiting For The Stars’
(P. Arbez/D. Shaw/J. Garraud)
The production of this video followed Health and Safety guidelines and Covid-related laws and regulations.
Bureau Veritas Italia monitored the set in which animals were present and verify that no animals were harmed.

node.text: Sterling silver jewelry is intricately designed with the Interlocking G motif on pieces that recall retro chain necklaces, reimagined through the Gucci lens to celebrate both past and present. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciJewelry

node.accessibility_caption: A shot of three models standing next to the trunk of a yellow car in the desert with hills and a grey sky in the background, (left to right) one styled with long auburn hair, wearing pince-nez round-frame glasses with a gold metal frame, gold metal chain and yellow lens, a red, ivory and black blazer with geometric print detailed with flowers and gold fringed appliqués, a matching shirt and matching pants, carrying a beige neo vintage GG Supreme canvas messenger bag with brown and yellow leather trims, brass hardware, and oval Gucci leather tag with feline head on one shoulder by the green and red Web stripe strap; one styled with short natural hair, wearing gold metal aviator glasses with light yellow lenses, a bright red and gold GG diagonal shirt with contrast stripe details, pussy bow neck, covered button placket, and bishop sleeves with long cuffs, and flared blue jeans, carrying a beige neo vintage GG Supreme canvas mini bag with brown and yellow leather trims, and oval Gucci leather tag with feline head across-body by the brown leather strap; one wearing an oversize brown leather blazer, oversize brown leather pants and beige lace shirt with brown trims, carrying a beige neo vintage GG Supreme canvas messenger bag with brown leather trims, brass hardware, and oval Gucci leather tag with feline head across-body by the green and red Web stripe strap.

node.text: Mini bags from the #GucciOuverture collection draw on vintage silhouettes while adding a contemporary note to practical accessories. Crafted from monogram canvas, the designs are embellished with an oval leather tag combining the brand's logo with a feline detail. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessando_michele

node.accessibility_caption: A close-up shot of two models’ hands resting on the hood of a gold-colored car, (left to right) one wearing black nail polish, a red shirt and a watch with a steel case, green and red bezel, green rubber crown, green dial with multi-icon indices, and a fabric Web strap; the other wearing a beige and blue striped shirt, blue sweater and a watch with a steel case and bracelet, green and red bezel, green rubber crown, and green dial with multi-icon indices.

node.text: The Gucci Dive watch is distinguished by a Web strap in a nod to the House’s equestrian heritage. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessando_michele #GucciTimepieces

node.text: Functional accessories take the form of GG canvas messenger bags and totes inspired by vintage luggage designs. The styles are trimmed in leather and detailed with the emblematic monogram of Guccio Gucci. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessando_michele #GucciOuverture

node.text: Storied symbol of the House, the Interlocking G appears on supple leather ballet flats from the #GucciOuverture collection as an original perforated motif decorating the toe. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessando_michele

node.text: Known for its half-moon shape, the #GucciJackie1961 is retold with a contemporary edge in smooth leather and GG canvas in beige and denim. The House staple is defined by the signature piston hardware that lends a recognizable finish. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessando_michele #GucciOuverture #GucciBeloved

node.text: Pick your favorite @guccibeauty shade. From matte to sheer, discover a range of brilliantly colored lipsticks in diverse formulations created to channel your inner self. More via link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeauty

node.text: An intense high-coverage varnish, @guccibeauty’s new plant-based nail lacquers are presented in ten vibrant shades, offering a long-lasting glossy shine. Inspired by vintage nail polish bottles, Vernis À Ongles is designed with a sleek ribbed grip handle, while the pear-shaped clear glass bottle is finished with Gucci lettering in gold. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeauty

node.text: As part of a series of colorful, playful images shot by @riccardo.apostolico for @guccibeauty: Fluide De Beauté Fini Naturel—a collection of natural finish liquid foundations available in 40 shades, Poudre De Beauté Mat Naturel, a buildable face powder that creates a unified complexion with a natural finish, and Poudre De Beauté Éclat Soleil to deliver a sun-kissed glow and a luminous looking finish. Discover more through link in bio. #AlessandroMichele @alessandro_michele #GucciBeauty
